articles.title: Caitlin Clark Scores 10 in Return from Groin Injury as Fever Lose to Valkyries - Bleacher Report
articles.description: The Golden State Valkyries spoiled Caitlin Clark's return as they beat the Indiana Fever 80-61 on Wednesday afternoon in Indianapolis.
